         <abstract id="aspace_beaa861d52ee75b88da753cf49c4e7c3">The collection consists of printed material relating to the political and social conditions in Burundi and a photograph of a Mubira woman with a lip disc.  </abstract>
         <langmaterial id="aspace_7c71e6799e22d15c35b56892e7b3dca4">
            <language>The materials are in English, French, and Rundi.</language>
         </langmaterial>
    
      </did>
