      </relatedmaterial>
      <arrangement id="aspace_506b4a6135162b25243d0146f95db66b">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The material in the first accession is arranged chronologically. Additions to the collection may vary in arrangement.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_d9377c5cef8d2900a3301f2f1cddc37e">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of printed material relating to the political and social conditions in Burundi and a photograph of a Mubira woman with a lip disc.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_e7c8acbdd0c40aa9d79de1e229b03b18">
